      <abstract encodinganalog="5203_">Collection includes materials relating to the Baldwin Sheep and Land Company and Hay Creek Ranch, collected by by Edwards. John Griffith Edwards was an Oregon sheep breeder, owner of Hay Creek Ranch, and partner in Baldwin Sheep and Land Company.</abstract>
      <langmaterial>
