    <bioghist encodinganalog="545" id="a2">
      <p>John Griffith Edwards was an Oregon sheep breeder, owner of Hay Creek Ranch, and partner in Baldwin Sheep and Land Company.</p>
    </bioghist>
    <scopecontent encodinganalog="520$a">
      <p>Typescript history of Baldwin Sheep and Land Company by Edwards, 8 pp; Newspaper clippings about the Baldwin Sheep and Land Company and Edwards; Correspondence relating to the company and Hay Creek Ranch; Financial records; Appointment documents; Stock record book for the company, 1 v, 1882-1889; Minutes of the Baldwin Sheep and Land Company, 1 v, 1887-1924.</p>
    </scopecontent>
